# NAME: Futu_Moomoo_QX
# DESC: Futu / Futubull / Moomoo consolidated rules
# FORMAT: Quantumult X rules
# POLICY: PolicyFutu
# UPDATED: 2026-06-13
# SOURCES: MetaCubeX meta-rules-dat, h8y/fly, blackmatrix7/ios_rule_script issue #1687, koo17173/rule-set where applicable
# NOTE: Domain rules are enabled. IP-CIDR rules are intentionally commented for later testing.
# NOTE: Covered child domains/subdomains and overlapping CIDR entries have been removed.

